history.content:
It seems that there is somehow still some confusion over the application deadline...

You must submit a completed application through the online application system by 8:59 PM PST March 15th, 2019. Late applications will not be accepted. Admissions decisions will be announced by early April by e-mail.

This includes ALL application materials (Transcript, SOP/PHS, LORs, CV/Resume, etc.)
history.subject: Reminder: EECS 5th Yr MS Deadline to apply -- 8:59 PM PST March 15th.
